\par First, the warded creatures gain a +4 deflection bonus to AC and a +4 resistance bonus to saves. This benefit applies against all attacks, not just against attacks by lawful creatures.
\par Second, the warded creatures gain SR 25 against lawful spells and spells cast by lawful creatures.
\par Third, the abjuration blocks possession and mental influence.
