\par In addition to the obvious effects, a blinded creature suffers a 50% miss chance in combat (all opponents have full concealment), loses any Dexterity bonus to AC, grants a +2 bonus to attackers\rquote 
 attack rolls (they are effectively invisible), moves at half speed, and suffers a \endash 4 penalty on Search checks and most Strength- and Dexterity-based skills.
